<title>LLVM backend</title>

<preface>

<p>Development of the <archname/> backend for the LLVM compiler:
<link href="https://github.com/bdpx/llvm-project">github.com/bdpx/llvm-project</link>.
</p>

</preface>

<section id="llvm_intro">
<title>LLVM backend intro</title>

<p>How to build/use.</p>

<table>
<caption><archname/>-specifiec LLC options</caption>
<thead><tr>
<th>Option</th>
<th>Default</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td>--postrisc-enable-block-merging</td><td>1</td><td>Enable fallthrough blocks merging.</td></tr>
<tr><td>--postrisc-enable-dense-calls</td><td>1</td><td>Enable calls inside bundle.</td></tr>
<tr><td>--postrisc-enable-move-merging</td><td>1</td><td>Enable mov2 merging.</td></tr>
<tr><td>--postrisc-enable-nullification</td><td>0</td><td>Enable nullification instructions.</td></tr>
<tr><td>--postrisc-enable-pre-post-update</td><td>0</td><td>Enable Pre/Post update instructions.</td></tr>
